# takeoff-ai: System Architecture Reference

## Purpose
takeoff-ai is a construction material takeoff SaaS that sends construction plan images/PDFs to Claude (claude-sonnet-4-6) via the Anthropic API and returns structured JSON material lists. It supports two distinct takeoff flows and three plan-type disciplines.

---

